# Scale Up Infrastructure

## Diagram
```mermaid
graph TD
    USER[User] --> DNS[DNS]
    DNS --> LB1[HAProxy Load Balancer 1]
    DNS --> LB2[HAProxy Load Balancer 2]

    LB1 <--> LB2

    LB1 --> WEB[Nginx Web Server Tier]
    LB2 --> WEB

    WEB --> APP[Application Server Tier]
    APP --> DB[(Dedicated MySQL Database Tier)]

## Explanation

* Two clustered load balancers improve redundancy
* Separate web tier handles HTTP traffic
* Separate app tier handles business logic
* Dedicated DB tier improves performance
* Infrastructure supports scaling by tier

## Benefits
* High availability
* Better scalability
* Easier maintenance
* Improved security
* Tier isolation

